e.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46cc9368fa64189746afe8450f47da61a68f2210","tid":11137,"uid":39912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:16:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa458ee80f59de967d271620e5e3fdcfec98e0a9","tid":11137,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:46:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f1bf0f7b4c2ada5f10aca7eabfd7a61ab3942f","tid":11137,"uid":2997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:02:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c4fc33e23c68118ccd728dd387ef3a4be131a41","tid":11137,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:07:04.000Z","msg":"佢話建國之後要處死梁天琦果陣係食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e657709c6a463df81367fc66099e03eb664082b5","tid":11137,"uid":2339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢話建國之後要處死梁天琦果陣係食左藥未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇睇尋日天琦講過啲乜嘢垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己endorse青政梁游，叫選民投佢哋即係投天琦自己，結果青政宣誓事件出事之時潛咗水，畀人DQ埋先至上水做網台節目，但居然話青政宣誓唔關佢事，光速割蓆，毫無承擔，亦背叛一眾投青政即投天琦嘅選民。<br />\n<br />\nEndorse青政，將本土派名聲一次過敗光。<br />\n面對人大釋法，青政DQ，就潛水唔理，扮乜鳩都唔清楚。<br />\n無事就拎光環，有事就話自己唔係有能力嘅領導者， 光速割蓆，推卸責任扮無辜。<br />\n<br />\n簡直就係禍港之孽，當然就要處死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0675f61591b2eca6d0c494b9ffbae8d56b794d99","tid":11137,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T03:21:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"526264370df0ea300b10a28a4806da62a5b1cd87","tid":11137,"uid":233